 Artemis::
Artemis transformed to her futuristic car mode and she followed JetV "Where you go?"said the femme
  gunthers@... wrote: Tremor continued running through the underbrush, grabbing the 
falled weapon that belonged to Slugslinger.  He made it to a small 
clearing where he jumped and flew through the air.  He made a 
direct line for his home base.
=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
JetV arrivedin the clearing just after Tremor took off.  "Slag, there is 
too much growth for me to be able to follow through the trees." he 
then opened a comm link to Crotale.  "Crotale, this is JetV, what is 
the Decepticons heading?"

Crotale paused for a second back at the Hidden One, then pointing 
him out on his internal scanners reported, "JetV, Crotale here.  
"His heading is 67.054 degrees west of north.  I can't follow him 
with my scanners for too far, my power levels are low."

"That's good enough for me big guy." JetV said as he hit the 
throttle.  His back wheels swerved on the ground then once straight 
again flew off through the trees dodging them quickly.
